# Senren Banka — Thai Translation toolkit
# This repo lives inside the GAME directory. To avoid ever committing
# copyrighted game assets (or multi-GB archives), we IGNORE EVERYTHING by
# default and then explicitly un-ignore only our own tools + translation data.

# 1) ignore every top-level entry
/*

# 2) un-ignore safe top-level files
!/.gitignore
!/README.md
!/LICENSE

# 3) tools/  — our pipeline scripts + guide (NOT the 3rd-party FreeMote binaries)
!/tools/
/tools/FreeMote/

# 4) thai_work/ — keep only our translation data + dashboards
!/thai_work/
/thai_work/*
!/thai_work/th/
!/thai_work/glossary.csv
!/thai_work/PROGRESS.md
!/thai_work/manifest.json
!/thai_work/progress.json

# 5) within th/: keep Thai translations (idx -> th), drop the source dumps
#    (*.src.tsv contain the original JP + official EN text = copyrighted)
/thai_work/th/*.src.tsv

# ---- NEVER commit (redundant with the whitelist, kept explicit for safety) ----
# *.xp3 / *.xp3.orig                game archives (Yuzusoft assets, multi-GB)
# thai_work/strings_cn.csv          master CSV (contains JP + official EN)
# thai_work/fonts/                  base/merged/variant font binaries (build locally)
# thai_work/{json_cn,psb_cn,pe_extract}/   decompiled scenarios (copyrighted)
# dataxp3/ scnxp3/ savedata/ ...    extracted game data
